title: Looking for a youtube editor

embed.description: A chiller from Brisbane. Sing or Rap, it's all music.

body:
Hey guys, 

I'm a singer/songwriter/rapper with a love for league. I've been having a lot of fun recently making songs about streamers and LCS games. I've made a song called 'Hardstuck in Gold' and would love to find a youtube video editor who would want to team up with me for this (and other videos hopefully). 

Little bit about myself:

In regards to league: I peaked at Diamond 2 and made a bit of money coaching low levels. I stopped taking the game as serious but I still play a whole lot. I am on very frequently.

Out of league: Toured down the east coast of Australia playing music. Lived in Melbourne for a few years now I live in Brisvegas. (Would be great if you lived near me. But with the wonders of the net it also wouldn't matter if you didn't.) Add me ingame to have a chat if you're keen. 

IGN: BlueLiquor
I added in my soundcloud link just for the lols.
